snippet.textDisplay:
Feb 1st:
over 11,000 cases identified with fatalities at 259.
This is spreading fast simply because it's jumping from person to person, and each carrier is not exhibiting symptoms at all for days after contracting and spreading. So it's like going on a speed dating binge with 400,000 hotels lined up for speed dating month, that goes on 24/7 and the hotels are connected by roads, railways, and of course air. And each person you shake hands with, each new introduction and 2 minute exchange of "dating" information is simply enough to spread the disease.
These numbers will grow. It will become endemic in the greater Chinese and Asian populations. It will sicken those that it can, kill those that it can, but it will not go away.
Easily 100,000 infected cased diagnosed by middle February and at the 2.1%-2.2% mortality rate about 2200 death.
But it's not going anywhere. So by Summer, 2020, it will go dormant, and just like the influenza (Flu) season, but it will be back next year.
I suppose another reason to seek alternative sources for business and food. Too risky placing all our eggs in China.

My theory is that the risk is mostly propaganda. I think it’s all engineered to run an experiment. Most wont know they’re in the experiment. So what do we have here?? A mutating disease that resembles most common illness and the only deaths are people who sought treatment? No one has posthumously been diagnosed. So I think it goes something like this (because remember protocols come from the top and there’s a lot of nefarious people at the top)..

Subject:“I think I have a bad cold dr.”

Dr:“Well you do but let’s get you to a specialist because you’ve said you’ve come in contact with someone or something from a region and I’ve been instructed that you need to see these people who can diagnose and treat you.”

Subject:“Ok”

And then the “specialists” infect you with a test model of their bio warfare disease.

I think this whole scare is part of the warfare. Its a phase of the bio weapon. “CoronaVirus” is from a bio warfare plant in the first place.

I’m just going to take my vitamins and go about my business. There’s no cure anyway.

So look it’s easy to label a disease by its symptoms and then control the populace with fear. It’s like saying the ‘poopymcpoopersVirus’ has escaped!! There are no distinguishing symptoms other than freckles.

Then You can bet a majority of the freckled people will be alarmed. Of those who are alarmed enough to go to the dr, there will be some who are sent to “specialists”. Because your hometown dr isn’t going to know enough based on the vague literature he’s been sent. And he would only falsely confirm because the literature says “freckles” and looks at you and sees either freckles or no freckles. He’s just going to follow protocol and send you to someone who “knows”.

But when he sends you to the specialists, a percentage of those are actually agents propping up the bio weapon. A percentage of drs will have obtained “training” so they feel validated with their qualification to be called a “specialists” but in reality they’re just there to provide the false positives which hide the actual bio weapon. Some people may graduate from their dr to a specialist to a treatment facility without ever gaining more freckles. But if you graduate from dr to specialist to treatment facility and then come across a “specialist”, you’re gonna get “treatment” and you might end up getting more “freckles” in the rush to trust people for the cure of ‘poopymcpoopersVirus’.

It’s ok to Laugh if you want but look what the stock did with this scare, there are plenty of reasons to be skeptical.

You’re gonna have to make your own choices whether or not to get diagnosed. I’ve been wrong about things before so I’m not making myself liable for whether or not you get treatment for CoronaVirus but I ask myself “Do I gotta know if I have the CoronaVirus since there’s no cure? If there’s no cure and the best thing to do is to ride it out then why wouldn’t I just ride it out assuming that it’s probably just a bad cold or flu?”

I’m not scared of The CoronaVirus. I’m scared of the evil minds that invented it.

It was invented. To what extent?

And that’s why I wrote this.
